name: Zach Woods
description:
On "The Office", Zach Woods played a gangly awkward weirdo.

On "Silicon Valley", Zach Woods plays a gangly awkward weirdo.

On "The Office", when Woods was on the screen, we cringed.

On "Silicon Valley", when Woods is on the screen, we cringe... and laugh.

On "The Office", Woods did not fit in.

On "Silicon Valley", Woods does not fit in â€” which makes him perfect on a show about people who don't really fit in.

On "The Office", Woods' character was forgettable.

On "Silicon Valley", Woods' character is anything but.

On "The Office", Woods' arrival coincided with the show's descent into irrelevance.

On "Silicon Valley"... alright, we made our point.
